    <summary>
      <span data-ttu-id="7afa3-101">識別由一個或多個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragment" /> 項目組成的 Story 開頭或結尾。</span>
      <span class="sxs-lookup">
        <span data-stu-id="7afa3-101">Identifies the start or end of story composed of one or more <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragment" /> elements.</span>
